<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Новости - Личный Блог</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #1a1a1a; /* dark grey background color */
            color: #FFFFFF; /* white text color */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
        }
        #container {
            width: 800px; /* Container width */
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #333333; /* Dark gray container background color */
            border: 2px solid #8A2BE2; /* Purple container border */
            border-radius: 10px; /* Rounded container corners */
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); /* Container shadow */
        }
        .post {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #8A2BE2;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #292929; /* Dark grey post background */
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto 10px;
            margin-left: 3px;
        }

        .post-content {
            max-height: 100px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .post-content.expanded {
            max-height: none;
        }

        .post-content {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .post-date {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #AAAAAA; /* Light gray date text color */
        }
        .post-user {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #CCCCCC; /* Light gray user text color */
        }
        #left-panel {
            flex: 1;
            background-color: #1a1a1a; /* Dark gray panel background */
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        #news-area {
            flex: 3;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .profile-icon {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #8A2BE2; /* Purple profile icon background */
            color: #FFFFFF;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .profile-icon img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .small-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            background-color: #8A2BE2; /* Purple button background */
            color: #FFFFFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        #input-area {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            margin-top: 50px;
            width: 500px;
            max-width: 900px;
            padding: 45px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #8A2BE2;
            border-radius: 5px;
            width: 300px;
            outline: none;
        }
        input[type="submit"] {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #8A2BE2;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-left: 15px;
        }

        #posts-container {
            max-height: 60vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .separator {
            position: absolute;
            width: 1px;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: #8A2BE2;
        }

        #separator1 {
            left: 25.33%;
        }

        #separator2 {
            left: 75.66%;
        }

        .post-avatar {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }
        .logout-icon {
            position: fixed;
            top: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            z-index: 9999;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="left-panel">
        <h2>VK.BEBRA.UA</h2>
        <div class="profile-icon">
            <img src="https://s.isanook.com/ga/0/ud/218/1093497/genshin-impact-(1).jpg?ip/crop/w670h402/q80/jpg" alt="Аватар">
        </div>
        <a href="link_to_profile.html" class="small-button">Перейти в профиль</a>
        <div>
            <h3>Случайные виджеты:</h3>
            <p>Случайный виджет 1</p>
            <p>Случайный виджет 2</p>
            <p>Случайный виджет 3</p>
            <!-- Добавьте больше виджетов по желанию -->
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="news-area">
        <h1>Новости Личного Блога</h1>
        <p>Здесь отображаются последние новости и статьи блога.</p>

        <div id="posts-container">
            {{#each posts}}
            <div class="post">
                <div class="post-user">
                    <img class="post-avatar" src="https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/1664610068472386993/AEFFCA6FA72E4F5FB2C80A78BE368EA641912EAC/?imw=512&&ima=fit&impolicy=Letterbox&imcolor=%23000000&letterbox=false" alt="User Avatar">
                    <p>{{name}}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="post-content">
                    <p>{{content}}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="post-date">
                    <p>{{date}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>

        <div id="input-area">
            <form action="/submit-comment" method="post">
                <input type="text" name="comment" placeholder="Напишите комментарий здесь">
                <input type="submit" value="Отправить">
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="separator1" class="separator"></div>
    <div id="separator2" class="separator"></div>

    <a href="/account/logout" class="logout-icon">
        <img src="https://cdn1.iconfinder.com/data/icons/heroicons-ui/24/logout-512.png" alt="Logout" style="width: 20px; height: 20px;">
    </a>
</body>
</html>